lead_paragraph: PRETORIA (Reuters - Sticking to their own brand of rugby and ignoring the exhausting altitude is going to be key to Australian success against South Africa in their Rugby Championship clash on Saturday, coach Michael Cheika said.

headline.print_headline: Rugby-Australia Must Stick to Their Game Plan in Pretoria: Cheika
headline.main: Rugby-Australia Must Stick to Their Game Plan in Pretoria: Cheika
